s ceux qui ont besoin de se loger rapidement,<br \/>\nsans investir trop d\u2019argent, pour une dur\u00e9e courte<br \/>\nou incertaine<\/li>\n<li>Salari\u00e9s en mobilit\u00e9 ou en contrat court<\/li>\n<li>Salari\u00e9s en formation<\/li>\n<li>Apprentis, alternants<\/li>\n<li>Jeunes d\u00e9butant dans la vie active<\/li>\n<li>Personnes et familles en situation de rebond<br \/>\napr\u00e8s une rupture personnelle ou sociale<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<h3>Les points cl\u00e9s<\/h3>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column]  <div class=\"in-skin-blocks-key-points\">\n    <div class=\"in-skin-blocks-key-points-content\">\n                              <div class=\"columns column-1 vc_col-xs-6 vc_col-sm-6 vc_col-md-3 vc_col-lg-3 \">\n          <div class=\"content\">\n                          <p class=\"in-skin-blocks-key-points-illustration\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"165\" height=\"213\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/picto-appart@3x.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/picto-appart@3x.png 165w, https:\/\/www.areli.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/picto-appart@3x-85x110.png 85w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 165px) 100vw, 165px\" \/><\/p>\n                                      <p class=\"in-skin-blocks-key-points-description\">Appartements pr\u00eats \u00e0 habiter, meubl\u00e9s et \u00e9quip\u00e9s<\/p>\n                      <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n                              <div class=\"columns column-1 vc_col-xs-6 vc_col-sm-6 vc_col-md-3 vc_col-lg-3 \">\n          <div class=\"content\">\n                          <p class=\"in-skin-blocks-key-points-illustration\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"165\" height=\"213\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/picto-apl@3x.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/picto